title: Paige Lilley

seo.title: Paige Lilley
seo.description: Paige Lilly's dance journey ignited at the tender age of 14 when she was first introduced to the captivating realm of Afro dance. Her talent quickly flourished, propelling her to secure a spot at The Brit School of Performing Arts.
